{"tid":1222193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如何同紅底人仕講反修例","createTime":"2019-06-14T11:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T16:39:55.000Z","uid":259928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6fcbb685d2632253398ae095ce2699f1833b0b9a","tid":1222193,"uid":259928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KeSu4GE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeSu4GE.jpg&h=36e5e7c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真喎，林鄭一出手，啟德地皮乖乖撤資111億，2500萬訂都唔要<br />\n佢揸英國護籍，一定係想英國借中英聯合聲明收番香港，而家連文翠珊都出口講，冇得假，我地要保一國兩制，香港係中國密不可分既一部分，唔可以俾英狗成功分列祖國<br />\n睇下最近搞到台灣又出口聲明唔肯回歸，明明個蔡英文都氣數以盡，隨時中國可以收番台灣，咁樣搞一搞又收唔成<br />\n修例絕對唔可以修得成，香港係國際大都會，俾佢修得成d外部勢力就會借機挾持香港撕列香港，中國同美狗打貿易戰，一定唔想自己屋企後門俾外部勢力搞，要一齊反修例，保憲法，撐經濟，保一國兩制"},{"pid":"f5849bb8bc0376a5709fa7bb5a7a36596f682f61","tid":1222193,"uid":259928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:21:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e9d360f01cb7db5b933cca049b939afa9833683c","tid":1222193,"uid":259928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d77607e510d3a27fb587e85123cedcd61185a85","tid":1222193,"uid":259928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc09ec9d592c2a95e78c56ea7a126cad9c79d560","tid":1222193,"uid":259928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T16:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}